    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>red wine paste</strong>, <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[455ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[650ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> harissa & red wine stock</strong></p>",
