      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 10 min, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>orzo</strong> and <strong>harissa & red wine stock </strong>to the dish with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and gently stir it all together</p>",
      "order": 5,
