    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> on top of the orzo and drizzle over your <strong>honey</strong></p><p>Season with a generous crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven for 18-20 min further or until the stock has been absorbed and the orzo is cooked with a slight bite – this is your <strong>baked harissa & red wine orzo with honey Greek cheese</strong></p>",
